The company is in it for the money.  They don't give a fuck about loyalty beyond the cost of turnover.  They don't give a fuck about employees but to get the most labor for the cheapest possible price.  I'm in it for my business, and I make the best decisions for my business.  Employees should be treated with respect just as much as companies.</div>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div>
<br />
BINGO.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		<!-- sig -->
			<div>
				__________________<br />
				<font face="Verdana">DAREVO OF THE DEAD</font> -- <font face="Palatino Linotype">48 Necromancer Druzzil Ro</font><br />
