		<div id="post_message_923123">Funny you post this..<br />
<br />
I was all set to start an EMT job on June 18, but yesterday tested and interviewed for an ambulance company elsewhere and got hired (I sent them my app. about a month ago).  Now I have to decide what job I am to take..<br />
<br />
Either job would be great, but I really want to work on the ambulance for a bit again.. on the other hand, if I turn down the position with the other company I am going to be burning some great bridges I have from working with them in the past.<br />
<br />
Best of luck to you in your decision, I know it's not easy and can be very nervewracking to have to turn down an employer.  Do what will best further you in your life and just explain that to them, and make sure you thank them for the consideration.</div>
